{"tid":605166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前加泰主席普伊格蒙特　在德國被捕","createTime":"2018-03-25T12:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T12:20:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf075cda41f0f780f8c30aaaf7252f93c449fe12","tid":605166,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180325/s00005/a23033ebbe1db316d5a1b0f7a15f8c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180325%2Fs00005%2Fa23033ebbe1db316d5a1b0f7a15f8c16.jpg&h=fba5c461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前加泰隆尼亞自治政府主席普伊格蒙特（Carles Puigdemont），周日早上在德國及丹麥接壤邊境地區，被德國警方帶走拘留。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙最高法院上周五宣布，決定以謀反罪名，起訴普伊格蒙特等13名爭取加泰獨立的領袖，並發出歐洲逮捕令。如果罪名成立，各人最高可被判監25年。<br />\n<br />\n普伊格蒙特去年10月底開始流亡比利時，上周四抵達芬蘭與當地議員會面。有議員透露，普氏在星期五晚上已離境。其代表律師則說，普伊格蒙特原打算返回比利時，但從丹麥過境德國時被德國警方拘捕。"},{"pid":"489f402824edf0115fb6b879642014ddae20d072","tid":605166,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c25ef31300ed919fffad787da25bce024ce5264","tid":605166,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489f402824edf0115fb6b879642014ddae20d072","tid":605166,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"兔唇仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}